  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study to characterize the steady-state pharmacokinetics of codeine and its metabolites
      morphine, morphine-3-glucuronide (M3G), and morphine-6-glucuronide (M6G) after oral
      administration of Roxane Laboratories' codeine sulfate tablets administered at a dose of 15
      mg Q4H x 5 days.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
